Kevin Bollaert, 28, was sentenced to 18 years in state prison for running a 'revenge porn' website that capitalized on the internet as a forum for public shaming .
He ran the site and moderated the site, called ugotposted.com, for more than 10,000 images of women sent in anonymously by people wanting to hurt them .
Victims were flown in from around the country to be involved in the prosecution .